snippet.title: Women's Health South Africa
snippet.description: The trusted source of information for women who want to be fitter, healthier and happier than ever. The magazine includes well-researched health features, results-oriented fitness and nutrition tips, down-to-earth fashion and beauty coverage and relevant advice on sex and relationships. There is no magazine in South Africa that speaks to women the way they speak to each other, and by the time readers put the magazine down, they'll feel like they've just had a conversation -- and a few laughs -- with their best friend.
